# 📖 DuoLector

**Free private app for long-distance couples.** Read books together, chat, draw, keep a shared diary, and send sealed letters — all in real time.

🌐 **[duolector.com](https://duolector.com)** · Works in Russia without VPN

---

## ✨ Features

| Feature | Description |
|---|---|
| 📚 **Synchronized Reader** | Both read the same PDF in real time. Page changes sync instantly. A floating bubble shows your partner's current page. |
| 💬 **Private Chat** | Real-time messaging with photo sharing and built-in translator (MyMemory API). |
| 📔 **Shared Diary** | Private entries only you two can see. React with emoji (long-press). Add photos. |
| 💌 **Sealed Letters** | Write letters that unlock on a specific date, when you meet, or with a password. See when your partner reads it. |
| 🎨 **Draw Together** | Shared canvas with real-time sync. Both draw at the same time. |
| 🎵 **Music Together** | Shared playlist with synchronized listening. |
| 🌐 **Translator** | Built into chat — select source and target language, translate in one tap. |
| ⏰ **Dual Clocks** | Shows your time and your partner's time zone (auto-detected). |
| 🔥 **Challenges** | Reading streaks, shared goals, and a km-based XP system. |
| 🔔 **Push Notifications** | Real-time alerts when your partner sends a message or letter. |

---

## 🛠️ Tech Stack

- **Frontend:** Single-file HTML PWA (vanilla JS, no framework)
- **Hosting:** GitHub Pages
- **Backend:** [Supabase](https://supabase.com) (PostgreSQL + Realtime + Storage + Auth + Edge Functions)
- **Auth:** Email/password + Google OAuth
- **Real-time sync:** Supabase Realtime (WebSockets)
- **AI proxy:** Supabase Edge Functions → Google Gemini (free tier)
- **Translation:** MyMemory API (free, no key required)
- **Push notifications:** Web Push API + VAPID
- **Languages:** ES 🇪🇸 · EN 🇬🇧 · RU 🇷🇺 · PT 🇧🇷 · FR 🇫🇷 · DE 🇩🇪

---

## 🏗️ Architecture

```
duolector.com (GitHub Pages)
│
├── index.html          ← entire app (single file)
├── manifest.json       ← PWA manifest
├── sw.js               ← service worker
├── privacy.html        ← privacy policy
├── terms.html          ← terms of service
└── .well-known/
    └── assetlinks.json ← TWA / Android verification

Supabase (sa-east-1, São Paulo)
│
├── Database (PostgreSQL + RLS)
│   ├── profiles
│   ├── couples / couple_members
│   ├── messages          (+ image_url)
│   ├── diary             (+ image_url)
│   ├── books / pages
│   ├── sealed_letters    (+ password + read receipts)
│   ├── journal_reactions
│   ├── reading_page_log  (anti-scroll validation)
│   ├── music
│   └── push_subscriptions
│
├── Storage
│   ├── pdfs              (books)
│   ├── photos            (chat + diary images)
│   └── music             (audio files)
│
└── Edge Functions
    ├── ai-proxy          (Gemini API proxy)
    ├── send-push         (Web Push notifications)
    └── alice-skill       (Yandex Alice / Алиса skill)
```

---

## 🚀 How It Works

1. One partner signs up at [duolector.com](https://duolector.com)
2. Copies their invite code from Settings
3. Shares it with their partner
4. Partner joins with the code — connected in seconds
5. Everything is private to that couple — no one else can see your data

---

## 📱 PWA Install

DuoLector is installable as a native app on any device:

- **Android:** Open in Chrome → "Add to Home Screen" / "Install App"
- **iOS:** Open in Safari → Share → "Add to Home Screen"
- **Desktop:** Chrome address bar → install icon

No app store required.

---

## 🌍 Why it works in Russia

Supabase servers are located in **São Paulo, Brazil** — not blocked in Russia. The app works perfectly in Yandex Browser and all other browsers without VPN.

---

## 🔒 Privacy & Security

- All data is isolated per couple using Supabase **Row Level Security (RLS)**
- Each couple can only access their own data
- No analytics cookies, no advertising
- PDF files and photos stored in private Supabase Storage buckets
- API keys are stored in Supabase Edge Function secrets — never exposed to the client

